data.description: Welcome to this charming 3 bedroom home with a fully finished basement, boasting 2 extra rooms in the basement. One of its standout features is the inviting front porch/sunroom, providing a serene spot to relax or work. You'll also appreciate the convenience of a two-car garage on the side.     This home is ideally located near the interstate, shopping, and schools. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this wonderful property your new home!
